                    "id": "PRRC_kwDOFcwZ1c5yHpip",
                    "body": "It's good to be explicit about what you're defining:\r\n```suggestion\r\nabbrev IsUpperTriangular [LT m] (M : Matrix m m R) : Prop := M.BlockTriangular id\r\n\r\n/-- The subtype of upper triangular matrices. -/\r\nabbrev UpperTriangular (m R) [LT m] [CommRing R] : Type _ := { M : Matrix m m R // M.IsUpperTriangular }\r\n```",
                    "createdAt": "2025-01-14T10:42:07Z",
